{"id": "ChIJGS22BPu5woARFx0PZQ0XDfE", "rating": 4.5, "userRatingCount": 379, "displayName": {"text": "DAMO", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJGS22BPu5woARFx0PZQ0XDfE/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT20xVE1qRTRPV3hWTlVsd2JWWlZabEp6UzJWNmVrRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "i visited damo from vancouver, canada, and honestly this is the best place for matcha and hojicha i tried so far in LA. service is very friendly and atmosphere is very chill so you can have a conversation or read a book! also the drinks are made with top quality ingredients so you can reflect it when you tasted it. also the shanghai mochi was the best one i tried so far. its crunchy from outside and so soft from inside, also flavor is well balanced. HIGHLY RECOMMENDED.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "i visited damo from vancouver, canada, and honestly this is the best place for matcha and hojicha i tried so far in LA. service is very friendly and atmosphere is very chill so you can have a conversation or read a book! also the drinks are made with top quality ingredients so you can reflect it when you tasted it. also the shanghai mochi was the best one i tried so far. its crunchy from outside and so soft from inside, also flavor is well balanced. HIGHLY RECOMMENDED.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "M S", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/115757523580329650712/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVG5g4NkqEMOD-Lf5ykRvcBEze7y25ZnXmoHT-eCQaF1kNoLxni=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-29T21:33:26.562324495Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT20xVE1qRTRPV3hWTlVsd2JWWlZabEp6UzJWNmVrRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT20xVE1qRTRPV3hWTlVsd2JWWlZabEp6UzJWNmVrRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2b9fb04b62d19:0xf10d170d650f1d17"}, {"name": "places/ChIJGS22BPu5woARFx0PZQ0XDfE/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2kwdGVuaGlTRlZyVjB0MlFWVTJjbUZWWTJkVFlVRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Cute little spot with affordable tea and matcha options! Friendly service, nice crowd. Enjoyed my matcha einspinner, definitely good quality matcha, amazing velvety foam.  8/10, would definitely come again!\n\n- : no wi-fi or charging outlets...", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Cute little spot with affordable tea and matcha options! Friendly service, nice crowd. Enjoyed my matcha einspinner, definitely good quality matcha, amazing velvety foam.  8/10, would definitely come again!\n\n- : no wi-fi or charging outlets...", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Maria Obry", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/114326836943556634083/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVOalVauka4W5Nzw4lg1ler7Hsu0chYR6n7c09Dk-QA1r6XoYY=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-21T19:49:11.744132038Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2kwdGVuaGlTRlZyVjB0MlFWVTJjbUZWWTJkVFlVRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2kwdGVuaGlTRlZyVjB0MlFWVTJjbUZWWTJkVFlVRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2b9fb04b62d19:0xf10d170d650f1d17"}, {"name": "places/ChIJGS22BPu5woARFx0PZQ0XDfE/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pSMk4yYzFlbUo0WVZSR01tUlZOVWxCY2pKQ1pGRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Damo is such a cool and inviting spot. The atmosphere is beautiful, and the staff were incredibly sweet—they took the time to explain the menu and gave great recommendations.\n\nThe matcha and coffee are both excellent, and you can really taste the quality. It’s a lovely place to relax and enjoy a well-crafted drink. Definitely worth a visit.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Damo is such a cool and inviting spot. The atmosphere is beautiful, and the staff were incredibly sweet—they took the time to explain the menu and gave great recommendations.\n\nThe matcha and coffee are both excellent, and you can really taste the quality. It’s a lovely place to relax and enjoy a well-crafted drink. Definitely worth a visit.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Lisset Graciano", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/107225728134805912441/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVN-UNzriE6kQfUFjHpRcUjWho4GkIANtTD91ZnjKR-GfvYf7Mn=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-06T06:08:36.640531323Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pSMk4yYzFlbUo0WVZSR01tUlZOVWxCY2pKQ1pGRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pSMk4yYzFlbUo0WVZSR01tUlZOVWxCY2pKQ1pGRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2b9fb04b62d19:0xf10d170d650f1d17"}, {"name": "places/ChIJGS22BPu5woARFx0PZQ0XDfE/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25GRmJHUjNiMm95VTNWTldVTTBTbUY0TVRJek5rRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Tasty drinks! I liked their matcha einspanner and their matcha strawberry too! The cream was really yummy. Their traditional Korean dessert set was just okay in my opinion but it might just be because I'm not particularly a huge fan of that type of dessert. I tend to like yakgwa though and theirs was just standard.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Tasty drinks! I liked their matcha einspanner and their matcha strawberry too! The cream was really yummy. Their traditional Korean dessert set was just okay in my opinion but it might just be because I'm not particularly a huge fan of that type of dessert. I tend to like yakgwa though and theirs was just standard.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Elaine Wang", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/108149311943287199389/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjULV3jTJ9wcLdbVooMhB0YHf-cWnf8R7T9Pu2c_tMQcF3dzPzq4Ww=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2026-01-21T03:01:58.556459601Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25GRmJHUjNiMm95VTNWTldVTTBTbUY0TVRJek5rRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25GRmJHUjNiMm95VTNWTldVTTBTbUY0TVRJek5rRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2b9fb04b62d19:0xf10d170d650f1d17"}, {"name": "places/ChIJGS22BPu5woARFx0PZQ0XDfE/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xvdFNGcHpUVlY2WTNwNlkyRkVlWGxDZVZkbFJGRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "I was in LA for a trip and decided to stop here after seeing many positive reviews online. I ordered the Strawberry Matcha Einspener with oat milk, and it was so delicious. I loved the thick cream top. The drink was perfectly sweetened and balanced; not bitter or overly sweet. The drink itself was beautifully layered and visually appealing.\n\nMy only negative is that it was $9.25 which is insane. I asked how many grams of matcha was in the drink so that I could know how much caffeine I was consuming (I told them that I typically use 3 to 4 g for myself when I make them at home), and the staff replied saying that they’re not allowed to disclose specific details, but they implied it’s WAYY more than that which was shocking lol. I’m assuming it’s at least double, so anywhere from 6 to 10 g, so caution if you’re sensitive to caffeine.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I was in LA for a trip and decided to stop here after seeing many positive reviews online. I ordered the Strawberry Matcha Einspener with oat milk, and it was so delicious. I loved the thick cream top. The drink was perfectly sweetened and balanced; not bitter or overly sweet. The drink itself was beautifully layered and visually appealing.\n\nMy only negative is that it was $9.25 which is insane. I asked how many grams of matcha was in the drink so that I could know how much caffeine I was consuming (I told them that I typically use 3 to 4 g for myself when I make them at home), and the staff replied saying that they’re not allowed to disclose specific details, but they implied it’s WAYY more than that which was shocking lol. I’m assuming it’s at least double, so anywhere from 6 to 10 g, so caution if you’re sensitive to caffeine.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Mimi", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/105515331820849065206/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWJLhJ4awzzE_NuIE3u8McrURJCBPnLIAgpTrioKeE5mgYfTyzI=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-28T05:07:42.712474110Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xvdFNGcHpUVlY2WTNwNlkyRkVlWGxDZVZkbFJGRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xvdFNGcHpUVlY2WTNwNlkyRkVlWGxDZVZkbFJGRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2b9fb04b62d19:0xf10d170d650f1d17"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJGS22BPu5woARFx0PZQ0XDfE/photos/AWCwydgcO3zjKnoTRi62CmCVdbVcb4C7xOREKUbfme0dumPpksFSL2edxDEMzW9h5FjnE6gD6VFZxO_NrAaVIEtF1wu8BMJcoeC6_rFQ1UiyGScPGCmRTADobqfZtV7cCJMr0gkGdF-8pxtbMLGwig6p8PAuP25vFu0cPE7reLHKQSIjensKmABXxlYHtoZPXxdaX92Ryts9VC5UjfP3MUoaQfwd0KhXXoOzULW2DfAwPsIW7bVtkJ-Cr9GBfcUBegApmOrhA6QzmeDetz9miU7bMDKus8ctYole73Fdr6CjxtXf8_BqflzMDeTBKtAUrafsK61QXbdeQhoQSGHtnVz5_TOeMGl_JxGMkyOTNdgjB0wYbQxLIaFsohhFwqM7a06nxRQPlK2d-tpa0OeJAkfSnegLgmNGofy7Q262y_TZm_ghp8UZvVf8CT4KcY3kEQ", "widthPx": 4000, "heightPx": 3000, "authorAttributions": [{"displayName": "Yung P", "uri": "https://maps.google.com/maps/contrib/10746